Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.78,0:00:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.20,0:00:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The bread I'd bought is gone and has\Nbeen replaced by three 100-yen coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.67,0:00:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do I take that as a sign of sincerity?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.34,0:00:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tohsaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.51,0:00:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tohsaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.97,0:00:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.10,0:00:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.48,0:00:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.73,0:00:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll just take a little longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.78,0:00:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shirou, how are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.83,0:00:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The numbness on my left side is gone.\NIt still feels a little heavy, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.29,0:00:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.21,0:01:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.30,0:01:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,'Morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.51,0:01:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to have slept\Nquite soundly last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.64,0:01:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not really. Somebody was\Nmaking noise past midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.60,0:01:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we're going out today.\NHurry up and get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Going out? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.69,0:01:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The next town over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.78,0:01:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.94,0:01:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What else? To go have fun, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.37,0:01:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a date, dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.53,0:01:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A date?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.70,0:01:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Between who and who?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.91,0:01:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Me and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.17,0:01:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay. You and I are—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.21,0:01:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.51,0:03:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shirou?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about you going on\Na date with Tohsaka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.60,0:03:19.98,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#12 The Final Decision
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is make-or-break time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.81,0:03:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop messing around. I don't know\Nwhat's going on here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.61,0:03:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look at you,\Ngetting all embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.11,0:03:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so jealous!\NOh, to be young and in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.74,0:03:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have a date today, too,\Ndon't you, Fujimura-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.66,0:03:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.91,0:03:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't want you two\Ngetting too crazy, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.17,0:03:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.05,0:03:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We should go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.51,0:03:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, where should we go?\NDo you two have any requests?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.86,0:04:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really think of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.61,0:04:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Should've known. And you, Saber?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.11,0:04:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I merely came along\Nas Shirou's guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.53,0:04:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please act as if I were not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Then you two are okay with\Ncompletely submitting to my plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so sinister!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.05,0:04:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I said I'd tag along with you,\Nnot go out on a date with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it would be nice\Nto take a breather.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:37.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- All three of us.\N- So sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.22,0:04:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But that's what the world\Ncalls a "date."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.43,0:04:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Girls hate guys who don't\Nknow when to give in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.23,0:04:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What girls, indeed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.82,0:04:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shirou.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:04:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, whatever! I'll tag along with\Nyou wherever you want, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.42,0:05:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Good, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.42,0:05:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't really taste like anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be like that!\NYou can tell it's sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.18,0:05:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it's sweeter than it looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.21,0:05:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.63,0:05:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.84,0:05:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're not bad, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.84,0:05:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. They make you\Nlook intellectual, Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.22,0:05:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.55,0:05:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Which ones next...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:06:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think these would\Nlook good on you, Saber.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.64,0:06:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looking good, Saber!\NAnd you try these on, Emiya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.11,0:06:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.66,0:06:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will never, ever wear glasses, got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.16,0:06:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I look young enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.29,0:06:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're self-conscious about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you have anything\Nto worry about, Emiya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're perfectly fine as-is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have to grow a little taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.93,0:06:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty average, I'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.10,0:06:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm nowhere near average! I have\Nto grow at least as tall as Issei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.36,0:06:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don't worry about it.\NYou'll grow a lot taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.57,0:06:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Based on what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.28,0:07:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you've got a solid build, so I bet\Nyou'll fill out if you eat right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.62,0:07:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With plenty of photosynthesis,\Nyou'll grow good and tall!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.67,0:07:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look like I have leaves?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, are you angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.55,0:07:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not really. I'll follow half of your advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.26,0:07:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't make you any promises\Nabout your height,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.93,0:07:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm sure you'll become\Na great-looking guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have my guarantee\Non that part, Shirou.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're blushing, you're blushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I love how everything is written\Non your face, Emiya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you're evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you get your kicks from teasing\Nguys in the same year as you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have the best reactions!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.12,0:07:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's stop playing with Shirou\Nand start on the main event!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Before lunch, let's knock\Na few out of the park!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:07:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.47,0:08:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That machine's set to 120kph...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.01,0:08:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shirou, what are you\Nstanding around for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.26,0:08:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I can't get one-upped\Nby Tohsaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.08,0:08:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Shirou? I find it uncomfortable\Nto be stared at in such a manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about hating to lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I miscalculated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea Saber would get\Nso obsessed with competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she gets angry if you go easy on her,\Nand sulks if you get too far ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.39,0:08:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You yourself were overcome with\Ncombativeness against Rin, Shirou!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When the person in the next cage answers\Nyou hit for hit, you get worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.27,0:09:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And seriously, you're way\Ntoo good at batting, Tohsaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you do pushups before\Ngoing to bed or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.33,0:09:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.12,0:09:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.54,0:09:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.21,0:09:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.05,0:09:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised. I had no idea\Nyou'd gone to all this trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.51,0:09:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. I asked you out,\Nso I had to pull out the stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.35,0:09:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this clears up one mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.98,0:09:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is what you used the bread for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I assumed you got hungry in the middle\Nof the night and ate the whole loaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.07,0:09:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emiya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your mouth, and let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.29,0:09:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:09:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the meal, Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.76,0:10:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What, you don't like spicy food, Shirou?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.47,0:10:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The seasoning is intense,\Nbut this is really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.85,0:10:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.69,0:10:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have some sauce\Non your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.98,0:10:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I get that for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.44,0:10:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why would you say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, maybe I took\Nthe joke too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I knew exactly the reaction\NI'd get, so I couldn't help myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.87,0:10:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever. But just you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.63,0:10:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be totally unflappable\Nstarting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.21,0:10:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that means I can go after you\Nwith no holds barred starting tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief! I was so sick\Nof taking it easy on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.02,0:10:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I take that back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.06,0:11:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll need a little more time, so if you could keep\Nit at our current level, that would be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.02,0:11:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really? If you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But when you're ready to\Nup your game, let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.53,0:11:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop pulling my punches\Nand knock you on your butt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.07,0:11:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You assume you'll win, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.07,0:11:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure that you aren't Satan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.83,0:11:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you're always wearing red.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.79,0:11:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to be feeling better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you back to normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.72,0:11:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tohsaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.85,0:11:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.01,0:11:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come over yesterday?\NTo say nothing of sleeping over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.35,0:11:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.52,0:11:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like it, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.31,0:11:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it might be\Na nice change of pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.44,0:11:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,True, it was fun to have\Nlots of people over yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.07,0:11:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.32,0:11:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It turned out to be\Nnothing, but thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.79,0:12:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't get the wrong idea!\NI wasn't concerned about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.17,0:12:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you'd be at a disadvantage\Nif you lost your partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.09,0:12:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you came to see how\NI was doing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.80,0:12:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's right!\NI'm glad that you see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.76,0:12:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.26,0:12:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you had up your sleeve,\Nbut you really were concerned, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.82,0:12:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That boy Shirou is going on\Ndates now, bold as can be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.24,0:12:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and get this, Kiritsugu-san.\NDo you remember a girl named Saber-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.00,0:12:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She says she's the daughter\Nof someone you knew abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.50,0:12:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She came all this way to visit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.63,0:12:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Abroad, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.93,0:12:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You never had a chance to take me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.71,0:13:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We made it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have fun today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We only got through half\Nof what I had planned,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.03,0:13:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but what did you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.34,0:13:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I haven't goofed around\Nlike that for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.55,0:13:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look, if you had fun,\Njust come out and say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's rude to me\Nafter playing host all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.52,0:13:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I didn't mean to be rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.23,0:13:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you did. You're subconsciously\Nslamming on the brakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.74,0:13:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what happened to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.82,0:13:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but if it was that bad, wouldn't your life\Nbe a lot happier if you let it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.54,0:14:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shirou, look outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.09,0:14:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.13,0:14:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, something is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.14,0:14:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.96,0:14:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.17,0:14:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get through to Archer.\NWe're completely sealed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.86,0:15:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These are—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.05,0:15:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is only serving to\Nincrease their number.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.51,0:15:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Precisely.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.01,0:15:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fighting within my bounded field will\Nonly expend your mana to no avail.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.85,0:15:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're pulling out all the stops for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As long as there's water, you have an\Nendless supply of troops, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.94,0:15:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We cut them off at the source, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.86,0:15:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How valiant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:16:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But perhaps you ought to look at this\Nbefore you raise your sword at me, Saber.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.37,0:16:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fuji-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.21,0:16:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you hope to accomplish\Nby taking a hostage?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.59,0:16:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have no business with you.\NMy interest lies in that boy there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.27,0:16:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your Magic Circuits are fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.35,0:16:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to take them\Nwithout killing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.69,0:16:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.06,0:16:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm resorting to these crude tactics\Nbecause I wish to win you over, not kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.53,0:16:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you become my puppet,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.32,0:16:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I shall refrain from\Nany further violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.95,0:16:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to you! You're doing all this\Nbehind your Master's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.66,0:16:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that jealousy I hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.71,0:16:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to disappoint you, but it is not\Nperfect omnipotence that I desire,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.17,0:16:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but rather imperfect, unique abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.76,0:17:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, boy, what is your answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.43,0:17:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such a difficult child.\NThis should be an easy decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how skilled your Saber is,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.81,0:17:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,she cannot defeat me with my\Nlimitless reserves of mana.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.94,0:17:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My power is being fed to me\Nby all the denizens of this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is as if I have\Nthousands of Masters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.91,0:17:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand\Nwhat I am saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.37,0:17:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't dare!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.33,0:17:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Even humans who are devoid\Nof mana still have souls, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.38,0:17:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We are soul eaters\Nby nature, are we not?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.67,0:17:42.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By stealing mana in the form\Nof life from these Masters,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.59,0:17:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can extract as much as I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.26,0:17:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, boy, you have\Nno chance of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.97,0:17:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Serve me with Saber.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.69,0:17:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Fuji-nee go...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.98,0:18:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Were you not paying attention?\NI said to surrender to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.91,0:18:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I will! Let Fuji-nee go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.12,0:18:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mean to say that you have no interest\Nin working with another Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.91,0:18:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, just not with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I seem to be on your bad side.\NThat really is a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Had you worked with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.13,0:18:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I would have been willing to\Nshare the Grail with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.01,0:18:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.64,0:18:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I promised myself that I'd\Nfight to stop people like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.44,0:18:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Grail has nothing\Nto do with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.28,0:18:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.03,0:18:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, did I touch a nerve?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.53,0:18:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you have only yourself to blame,\Nsaying things that you don't mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.79,0:18:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you yourself\Nare a victim of the Grail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.91,0:18:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with the Grail?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:19:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When you say those words, is it\Nnot out of hatred towards it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.96,0:19:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shirou?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.92,0:19:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know everything, Emiya Shirou.\NYou lost everything in the last war.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.85,0:19:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were found by Emiya Kiritsugu as you\Nwere alone in the flames, waiting to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.98,0:19:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How you must have suffered, being made his\Nson solely for the purpose of the next war
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.69,0:19:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and having magic forced upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.82,0:19:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way... Emiya-kun? Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.12,0:19:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the Grail has always\Nbeen a hated enemy to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.54,0:19:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is for that very reason\Nthat you have every right
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.75,0:19:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to claim the Grail as recompense\Nfor ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.92,0:19:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the Grail is as good as mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.26,0:19:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It would be child's play\Nto grant you your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.26,0:19:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You speak nonsense, Caster!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.01,0:19:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Grail will not appear until\Nbut one Servant remains!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.44,0:20:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, there is a way to claim\Nthe Grail without fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.90,0:20:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As a Caster, I can sense the\Ninner workings of the Grail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.32,0:20:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, if you, with your massive\Nmana output, were to assist me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.04,0:20:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I could summon the Grail right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.54,0:20:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is your last chance, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.59,0:20:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You wish to avoid\Nsenseless fighting, do you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.38,0:20:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then serve me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.55,0:20:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber's Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.85,0:20:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't go along with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.69,0:20:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you mad? Do you understand\Nthe position you are in?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.48,0:20:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't help a witch\Nwho treats people as food.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.30,0:20:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your methods are wrong.\NAnd one more thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't forced to become a mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.62,0:21:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I made the choice on my own to\Nfollow in my old man's footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.46,0:21:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Witch... You called me a witch?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.88,0:21:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I have no use for you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.09,0:21:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Die here, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.34,0:21:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.30,0:21:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move, Saber!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.10,0:21:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you.\NStay where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.93,0:21:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shirou, but she—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.94,0:21:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my. I had thought that\Nyou were utterly irrational,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.62,0:21:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but you do understand\Nyour situation, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.99,0:21:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Coward! You're going to kill\NShirou in cold blood?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.54,0:21:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not. I'm merely going to strip\Nhim of his status as a Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.63,0:21:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You will not join me,\Nbut you wish to save this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.72,0:21:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That tells me that you are prepared\Nto hand over your Command Seals.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.14,0:22:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right. How do I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.39,0:22:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shirou, no! Even if you\Ndo that, she will still—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.52,0:22:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will take them,\Narm and all, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.40,0:22:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That is enough, Shirou. I cannot allow you\Nto continue to play into Caster's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.82,0:22:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.53,0:22:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, do you honestly think she's the\Nsort who would release a hostage?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.71,0:22:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take it. That's all you want, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.84,0:22:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shirou!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.67,0:22:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to go to\Nsuch extremes to help others!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.05,0:22:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.72,0:22:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If my arm will save Fuji-nee's life,\NI don't have to think twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.31,0:22:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You truly are a foolish child!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.11,0:22:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are a nuisance, so die!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.37,0:23:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.45,0:23:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.39,0:23:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.94,0:23:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.57,0:23:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is my Noble Phantasm, Rule Breaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.49,0:23:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It nullifies any and all magic\Ncast in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.75,0:23:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The dagger of betrayal and denial.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.25,0:23:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The pact has been forged.\NI am now your Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.96,0:23:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are now as I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.34,0:23:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Betray your Master and pledge\Nyour blade to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.39,0:24:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You... You're a Servant,\Nand you've taken a Servant?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.93,0:24:10.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I have made her my familiar.\NSaber now belongs to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.56,0:24:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And now, here is your\Nfriend back, little fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.32,0:24:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fuji-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.03,0:24:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fuji-nee! Are you okay? Fuji-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.82,0:24:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fuji-nee...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.33,0:24:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I think I shall let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.54,0:24:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That show you put on was so wonderful\Nit was almost annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.59,0:24:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.50,0:24:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. I suppose that's how\Nthese things usually work.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.34,0:24:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Playtime is now over, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.72,0:24:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Saber. Strike down Archer's Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.48,0:24:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Never... Who would obey\Nthe likes of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.61,0:24:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, you will obey, Saber.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.15,0:24:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I have these\NCommand Seals,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.99,0:25:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you cannot defy me\Nin either body or soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.25,0:25:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Why did you do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.13,0:25:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.47,0:25:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Such a waste.\NThat boy was so fascinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.89,0:25:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Obey my Command Seal, Saber.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.94,0:25:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...run...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.19,0:25:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Shirou!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.61,0:25:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have to get Fuji-nee...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.49,0:25:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.41,0:25:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.53,0:25:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber's magic resistance is even effective\Nagainst the binding of a Command Seal?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.16,0:25:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But be that as it may,\NI won't let you escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.19,0:26:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.52,0:26:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.98,0:26:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Breaking through that\Nbounded field took quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.49,0:26:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From the inside, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.07,0:26:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Archer, take Fujimura-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.66,0:26:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, while we still can!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.79,0:26:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.15,0:27:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This was for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.44,0:27:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At least you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.53,0:27:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For now, get some rest, Emiya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.25,0:27:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see. While I was breaking through\Nthat field, Saber was taken.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.50,0:27:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's all you have to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.21,0:27:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes. But we should count our\Nblessings that we now know{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.84,0:27:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}what Caster's Noble Phantasm is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.89,0:27:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That Caster... Always sloppy\Non the follow-through.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.47,0:27:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Deep down, she might\Nactually be a decent woman.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.14,0:27:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem very concerned, Archer.\NWeren't you rooting for Saber?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.53,0:27:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't recall ever giving that impression.\NWhat makes you think that, Rin?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.66,0:27:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Would you believe\Nwomen's intuition?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.79,0:27:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.66,0:27:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you even old enough\Nto qualify as a woman?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.87,0:28:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For starters, you are lacking\Nin feminine charms.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.63,0:28:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In refinement, as well.\NAnd in addition...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.30,0:28:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and this is the most damning.\NYour appeal is hard to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.81,0:28:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well. You've finally\Nfound your groove again...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.40,0:28:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,... haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.53,0:28:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Getting back to the topic at hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.36,0:28:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,here's damning evidence #1\Nthat you were rooting for Saber:
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.95,0:28:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The first time you met Saber,\Nyou went easy on her, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.37,0:28:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how powerful Saber is,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.37,0:28:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt she could have gotten the better\Nof you, not with your defenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.96,0:28:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She caught me unawares.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.59,0:28:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like you, I'm vulnerable\Nto unexpected developments.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.84,0:28:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, get off my case.\NDamning evidence #2:
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.60,0:28:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After the incident with Rider, you tried\Nto provoke Saber, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.73,0:29:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was out of character\Nfor you, no two ways about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.90,0:29:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But when I looked at it from another\Nangle, it made perfect sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.44,0:29:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were actually scolding Saber, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.24,0:29:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right? I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.62,0:29:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if you two knew each\Nother in a previous life or what,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.62,0:29:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but it's unusual for you\Nto be so cold to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.54,0:29:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it? I think that I respond\Nto everyone in that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.42,0:29:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It only looks that way to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.72,0:29:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The way I see it,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.13,0:29:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you're only awkward when it comes\Nto things dealing with yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.39,0:29:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're smooth when it comes to others,\Nwhich is why no one notices.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.35,0:29:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, have you finally remembered?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.15,0:29:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what land's\NHeroic Spirit you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.02,0:29:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you have some\Nconnection to Saber,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.82,0:29:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you ought to be from an era\Nthat's close to hers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.36,0:29:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, everything is still hazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.66,0:30:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But as you say, I do have\Nmemories of this Saber.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.04,0:30:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But she does not seem to know me, so\Nwe could not have been very close.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.88,0:30:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.59,0:30:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,More to the point, Rin, how is\Nthe visitor you brought here?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.88,0:30:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Luckily, she missed anything vital.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.55,0:30:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But his wounds aren't\Nhealing at all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.18,0:30:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Their pact has been broken,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.68,0:30:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so he might have lost the healing ability\Nhe'd been getting from Saber.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.60,0:30:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, not him. I meant the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.44,0:30:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Fujimura-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.99,0:30:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Caster seems to have put her\Nunder a sleeping spell,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.53,0:30:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but she has lots of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.12,0:30:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've treated her, so she could sleep\Na whole week with no problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.92,0:30:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing Fujimura-sensei, she might\Njump out of bed any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.13,0:30:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps, but what that woman casts\Nare more curse than spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.88,0:30:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The simplest way to break it\Nis to kill the person who cast it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.47,0:30:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.52,0:31:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Defeating Caster is our top priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.44,0:31:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.94,0:31:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If possible, I want to do it before Saber\Nfalls completely under her control.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.62,0:31:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.20,0:31:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So your pact with that boy\Nis also over, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.08,0:31:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.29,0:31:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me "what?" Emiya Shirou\Nis no longer a Master, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.79,0:31:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.38,0:31:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Surely you aren't going to say\Nthat you mean to look after him
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.59,0:31:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,as a fallen brother in arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.26,0:31:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hardly. I'm not that big a softie.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.06,0:31:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.35,0:31:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.69,0:31:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My promise still stands until he himself\Nsays that he wants out of the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.02,0:31:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can reject him all I want,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.44,0:31:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but nothing is over until\Nhe says he wants out.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.53,0:32:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rin...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.20,0:32:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's our course of action. Do you\Nhave a problem with it, Archer?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.46,0:32:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What else can I do? I know painfully well\Nthat you are that sort of person.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.34,0:32:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Archer!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.60,0:32:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.44,0:32:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.82,0:32:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's... here?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.25,0:32:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Which means that she's out there\Nby herself right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.43,0:33:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... I made a mess... Tohsaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.48,0:33:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.19,0:33:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,looks familiar...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.99,0:33:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. It's the same as\Nthe one from that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.07,0:33:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, come on! Why are you here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.08,0:33:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why did you have to pick this hour\Non this day to be here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.37,0:33:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's still a way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.63,0:33:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Crap... What's she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.22,0:33:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's always going on about\Ndebts and favors,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.93,0:33:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but this is one debt\Nthat I can never repay!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.73,0:34:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tohsaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.58,0:34:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening, Assassin?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.88,0:34:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I said that I want you to continue\Nguarding the front gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.80,0:34:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There was an intruder, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.88,0:34:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I spotted an unusual bird,\Nso I struck it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.05,0:34:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is this something used by your kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.56,0:34:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is a familiar used for spying.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.15,0:34:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That young lady has terrible luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.81,0:34:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If she were slightly less talented,\NI would have taken her on as my pupil.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.36,0:34:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I leave my Master's defense to you, Assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.24,0:34:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guard the gate with your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.66,0:34:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, this person whom you address\Nas Kojiro does not truly feel alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.04,0:35:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ordering such a person to do anything to\Nthe death is meaningless, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.21,0:35:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't quibble.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.09,0:35:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are a Servant\Nthat I summoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.13,0:35:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you cannot pledge fealty to your lord,\NI shall simply eliminate you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.14,0:35:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Goodness me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.73,0:35:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My life is as insubstantial\Nas the shimmering heat haze,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.60,0:35:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I would rather it not\Nbe extinguished just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.61,0:35:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I do have\Na promise to keep.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.74,0:35:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then hold your tongue. Your only\Nconcern is guarding this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.66,0:35:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then guard it I shall.\NBut is this wise, Caster?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.58,0:35:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am also disloyal to my lord, but you are\Nacting on your own authority far too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.79,0:35:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your errand tonight is also without\Nyour Master's knowledge, I'd wager.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.01,0:35:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Day by day, you overstep your\Nbounds ever further, Caster...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.02,0:35:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Silence. The next time you\Nmake me repeat myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.98,0:36:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll eliminate you without\Nwaiting out the next five days.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.40,0:36:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear... The saying that women and\Nshort men are difficult to manage
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.11,0:36:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is true, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.58,0:36:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Worry not, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.12,0:36:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All is to be carried out without\Nyour Master's knowledge, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.04,0:36:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yours is a touching tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.42,0:36:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I only hope that your love for your\Nlord gets through to the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.01,0:36:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Assassin, mind your—
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.01,0:36:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am a sore loser.\NAllow me these poor jests.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.68,0:36:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On my blade,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.43,0:36:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I swear I shall protect this gate\Nfrom all, no matter who they be.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.23,0:36:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.65,0:36:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You do not trust my protection?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.19,0:36:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not. You are merely my insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.20,0:36:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I no longer require that, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.03,0:36:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With Saber now mine, I no longer need\Nto make this rustic place my temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.12,0:36:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A change of position?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.91,0:37:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning that you have\Nno further use for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.13,0:37:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is a sacred spot\Nsuperior to this mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.88,0:37:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, there is a place that\Nsuits me perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.01,0:37:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am leaving to claim my prize early.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.51,0:37:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I now have a new fortification, the Grail,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.27,0:37:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and even a new pawn in the form of Saber.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.27,0:37:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With all these, even my reticent Master
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.94,0:37:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,will be unable to offer up any\Nobjections to my plan of action.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.19,0:37:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Once I have the Grail,\NI will have nothing to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.28,0:37:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, for then no one will be able to stand\Nagainst me, no matter who they may be!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.80,0:37:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Caster.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.26,0:38:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have we met before, my good\Noverseer of this mad ritual?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.43,0:38:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want, Caster?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.56,0:38:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This place is inviolable\Nneutral territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.52,0:38:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of what Heroic Spirit they\Nmay be, no Servant may enter this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.82,0:38:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The rules have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.12,0:38:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Command Seals?!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.75,0:38:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.21,0:38:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber is now my puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.63,0:38:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You understand what\Nthat means, I take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.22,0:38:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The outcome of this war\Nis as good as decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.14,0:38:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something wrong with\Ncoming to claim my prize early?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.56,0:38:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed there is. The Grail will not appear\Nuntil but one Servant remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.06,0:38:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As a Servant, surely you were made aware\Nof this at the time of your summoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.07,0:38:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the Grail did say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.03,0:38:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It ordered me to go forth and slay the other\NHeroic Spirits to activate the Grail.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.32,0:38:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.49,0:39:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that refers to the Greater Grail, does it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.50,0:39:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, where is the Lesser Grail?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.71,0:39:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You priests are in charge\Nof the Grail's key, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.71,0:39:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is no Holy Grail here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.05,0:39:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wish to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.89,0:39:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make idle threats.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.97,0:39:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You betray yourself, Princess of Colchis.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.27,0:39:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You still have no stomach for brutality, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.08,0:40:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You just want me to stand by\Nand watch, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.88,0:40:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No one's going to interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.68,0:40:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This era has fine warriors, too, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.77,0:40:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But how long will his luck\Nhold out, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.88,0:41:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tohsaka... Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.40,0:41:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.33,0:41:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.12,0:41:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you're trying to prove,\Nbut you're being a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.16,0:41:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't leave. I promised that I'd\Nfight alongside you, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.46,0:41:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about that stupid promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.51,0:42:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what can you\Npossibly do as you are now?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.93,0:42:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've lost Saber.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.26,0:42:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.39,0:42:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, there's no need\Nfor you to fight now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.73,0:42:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a Master anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.85,0:42:16.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take shelter in the church,\Nand you'll be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.02,0:42:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid! I can't\Nleave Saber like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.69,0:42:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So no matter what, I'm gonna\Nfight to the bitter en—
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.24,0:42:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.03,0:42:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but that's what happens without her.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.66,0:42:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've had Saber to help you until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.38,0:42:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, for all your\Ntalk about Saber,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.46,0:42:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,what happens to her is none\Nof your concern now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.51,0:42:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong.\NEven if I'm not a Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.72,0:42:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber hated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.10,0:42:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way am I gonna let her be\Nthe stooge of somebody like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.02,0:42:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.69,0:42:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The problem is, you're powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.77,0:43:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you refuse to admit it,\Nlet me spell it out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.90,0:43:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The way you are now, you can't\Ndo anything to help Saber.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.87,0:43:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there is to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.87,0:43:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've lost Saber, and you're\Nno longer a Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.96,0:43:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no more reason for you\Nto be involved in the Holy Grail War,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.59,0:43:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so bow out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.63,0:43:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not so fast, Tohsaka.\NEven if that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.02,0:43:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot, what are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.47,0:44:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of this from now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.05,0:44:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.11,0:47:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you believe to the bitter end\Nthat you're right?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.78,0:47:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I comprehend the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.86,0:47:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Has the matter outside been resolved?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.87,0:47:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shirou, get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.20,0:47:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You protected me of your own\Nfree will, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.33,0:47:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let us reenact a battle out of myth!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.42,0:47:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Archer...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.84,0:47:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're... You can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.52,0:47:40.00,Next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Broadcast Starts April 2015
